{"tid":2238292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【專訪】林超英：如果我係秦始皇管香港，我禁咗冷氣佢！","createTime":"2020-10-11T04:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T05:24:29.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"679de7c262889e4b0ae60a99d6db7d5504d20cf3","tid":2238292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"【專訪】林超英：如果我係秦始皇管香港，我禁咗冷氣佢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%9E%97%E8%B6%85%E8%8B%B1-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%91%E4%BF%82%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87%E7%AE%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%88%91%E7%A6%81%E5%92%97%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%E4%BD%A2/?fbclid=IwAR3F2bMmDtYh95vB3V94lcbyWK2YCvNk0kUnyv_1KK30eWmsfZltKq-mRjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%25A7%25A6%25E5%25A7%258B%25E7%259A%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2592%2597%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E4%25BD%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3F2bMmDtYh95vB3V94lcbyWK2YCvNk0kUnyv_1KK30eWmsfZltKq-mRjE&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7804cdd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%25A7%25A6%25E5%25A7%258B%25E7%259A%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2592%2597%25E5%2586%25B7%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E4%25BD%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3F2bMmDtYh95vB3V94lcbyWK2YCvNk0kUnyv_1KK30eWmsfZltKq-mRjE&h=2a342db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%9E%97%E8%B6%85%E8%8B%B1-%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%91%E4%BF%82%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87%E7%AE%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%88%91%E7%A6%81%E5%92%97%E5%86%B7%E6%B0%A3%E4%BD%A2/?fbclid=IwAR3F2bMmDtYh95vB3V94lcbyWK2YCvNk0kUnyv_1KK30eWmsfZltKq-mRjE</a><br />\n<br />\n//一見到記者，安坐在辦公室的林超英就問：「要唔要開冷氣呀？睇你好辛苦喎！」的確，記者「滴緊水」幾乎褲都濕埋，但心想林超英不是堅持不開冷氣，更與環境局局長黃錦星鬥低電費嗎？所以禮貌但少少無奈地回答：「坐低就會涼㗎喇。」他心知記者在想甚麼，便說：「唔係個個都頂得順嘅，我哋睇吓幾多度先再決定開唔開。」一看那個有點歷史的酒精溫度計， 29&deg;C 有多，林超英立即跑去開冷氣。事實上，辦公室早已下了直簾開著風扇，西斜下根本一點陽光也照不進來，確實已比室外涼得多。<br />\n<br />\n林超英立即解釋，自己關心環保，但並非「環保塔利班」，有需要都會開冷氣，只是大家要考慮的是「應用則用」。//<br />\n<br />\n//等政府負責任搞環保，林超英形容「死得喇」，但個人層面又可以點緩減氣候變化？記者問他如果要選 3 個個人最有效且可實踐的減碳行為，林超英劈頭就說：「如果我係秦始皇管香港，我禁咗冷氣佢！」語氣似足「環保塔利班」，但他補充禁止之前有很多前提工夫要做，例如給予時間建築物規格要有促進自然通風的設計，亦要避免太多陽光入屋。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EV1afM2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEV1afM2.png&h=6e4c3a02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5372fac077e2b958c71d396bb47f496f53e917f9","tid":2238292,"uid":136416,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"林峰秦皇低能笑.gif<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a86ad7450791fc5321aeec8da4d34b6065bb090c","tid":2238292,"uid":5205,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"秦始皇 :全個中國都要開冷氣"},{"pid":"efb0d8bd6767bf3026c8dd3a09026c37db98ee58","tid":2238292,"uid":34065,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"如果我係秦始皇管香港，我禁咗冷氣佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔去搞工廠排廢氣?<br />\n支那個堆垃圾廠 你熄乜撚都無用啦"},{"pid":"9da645307c20f63a94bf6056e1b9301f6dd16996","tid":2238292,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c5217acba42ab04a0ad78b00815a961a6e30b5"